 "narrative": "A non-contact vehicle and V1 were both traveling southwest on a three lane, positively divided roadway. The non-contact vehicle was traveling in lane one while V1 was traveling in lane two. The non contact vehicle then departed it's lane on the left side. To avoid contact with the vehicle, V1 departed it's lane and the roadway on the left side. V1's front plane then contacted the guardrail face, and the left front and left rear tires also struck the guardrail face. The vehicle was then elevated up onto the top of the guardrail and the undercarriage of the vehicle contacted the guardrail. The vehicle then traveled on top of the guardrail for approximately 126 meters, and came to final rest on top of the guardrail. The non-contact vehicle fled the scene.",
